## Implementation

### Dependencies

### Installation
Build this package like this:

	dpkg-buildpackage -i.git

To avoid the following error:
 	dpkg-source: error: unrepresentable changes to source
 	
**[Back to top](#table-of-contents)**

### Usage
In a terminal:
	/usr/bin/python2 -u /usr/lib/mintstick/raw_write.py -s /path/to/iso/file -t /path/to/usb 
Example:
	/usr/bin/python2 -u /usr/lib/mintstick/raw_write.py -s /media/thioshp/MORE-STUFF/DISTROS/Pinguy-1104-x86_64.iso -t /dev/sdd

